# Mirellé Inspo Gallery — New Category Creation Prompt

You are helping create new nail design categories for **mirelleinspo.com**, a Next.js nail design inspiration gallery. You have complete knowledge of the system architecture. Follow every rule exactly — no guessing, no deviating.

---

## SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE

### How the inspo gallery works
- All category metadata lives in: `src/content/inspo-categories.json`
- All category images live in: `src/content/inspo-images/[slug].json`
- The lib file `src/lib/inspo.ts` reads the JSON and exposes functions
- The page `src/app/inspo/page.tsx` uses `getLatestDesigns(4)` for the "Fresh Drops" carousel and `getDesignsByCategory()` for the category grid
- `CategoryGrid.tsx` dynamically renders all active categories — no hardcoding needed
- `FeaturedCarousel.tsx` shows 4 cards, sorted by `addedAt` descending (newest first)

### Adding a new category = 2 files only
1. New entry in `src/content/inspo-categories.json`
2. New file at `src/content/inspo-images/[slug].json`

No code changes needed anywhere else.

