## FILE 2: inspo-images/[slug].json

Create at: `src/content/inspo-images/[slug].json`

### Complete schema:

```json
{
  "images": [
    {
      "id": "[slug]-001",
      "url": "/inspo/[slug]/[descriptive-filename].webp",
      "alt": "[descriptive alt text for SEO and accessibility]",
      "category": "[slug-without-year]",
      "isPremium": false,
      "dimensions": {
        "width": 1080,
        "height": 1920,
        "aspectRatio": "9:16"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

### Image field rules:

| Field | Rule |
|---|---|
| `id` | `[slug]-001`, `[slug]-002` etc — zero-padded 3 digits |
| `url` | `/inspo/[slug]/[filename].webp` — folder name must match slug exactly |
| `alt` | descriptive, keyword-rich, 15-25 words, no quotes — describes color + style + finish + occasion |
| `category` | slug without year suffix e.g. `almond`, `summer`, `french-tip` |
| `isPremium` | `false` for most, `true` for statement/embellished designs (max 20% of images) |
| `dimensions.width/height` | use actual dimensions — 1080x1920 for portrait (most common), 1080x1080 for square, 1920x1080 for landscape |
| `aspectRatio` | must match dimensions: `"9:16"` for portrait, `"1:1"` for square, `"16:9"` for landscape |

### Alt text formula:
`[color] [shape/style] [finish] nails [descriptor] creating [effect] [occasion] [purpose]`

Example: `"Coral almond nails summer bright with vibrant tropical creating vacation manicure perfect for beach getaway"`

### Minimum images per category: 20
### Recommended: 30-50 images

