## IMAGE FILE NAMING CONVENTION

Images live in: `/public/inspo/[slug]/`

Filename format: `[color]-[style]-[slug-base]-[descriptor]-[keywords].webp`

Examples from `almond-nails-2026`:
- `nude-chrome-almond-nails-soft-shimmer-elegant-professional-office.webp`
- `milky-white-almond-gel-nails-quiet-luxury-minimalist-aesthetic.webp`
- `chrome-pink-almond-metallic-finish-trendy-modern-statement-nails.webp`

Rules:
- All lowercase
- Hyphens only, no spaces or underscores
- Include color + style + key descriptors
- Always end in `.webp`
- Keyword-rich for image SEO

